quran[49]{c,v,t}:
  15,1,Alif-Lâm-Râ. Aga ni ma Ȃya ga m’Chitabu (cha Qur’an) soni ni Chisoomo chakupikanika
  15,2,Kakajinji katakaŵe achimakafili (ndema jatakaŵe ku Moto) ali nkulajila kuti bola angaŵe Asilamu (paŵaliji ku duniya)
  15,3,"Mwalekani agambeje kulya ni kusengwa, ni kwaluyaluya liganichisya (lyakupata yambone kwa Allah), basi taachiika kumanyilila (mbesi ja ukafili wao)"
  15,4,Ni nganituujonanjeje musi uliose ikaŵeje waliji wana chilamusi chakwe chakumanyika (cha ndema jakuujonanjila)
  15,5,Nkutula uliose nganiuŵa ujilongolele ndema jakwe (jakuwila) kapena kujichelewasya (jili jikwanile)
  15,6,"(Achimakafili) ni ŵatite (pakun’gamba Muhammadi ﷺ): “E mmwe aŵala ŵachintuluchile Chikumbusyo (Qur’an)! Chisimu mmwejo ŵamasoka.”"
  15,7,“Uli ngaikanago kukwetu Malaika naga n’di mwa akuŵecheta yakuona?”
  15,8,"(Allah akwasalila kuti): Uwwe ŵangatulusya Malaika ikaŵeje mwakuonaonape (kwisa kupeleka ipotesi), soni pajele ndemajo ngaakasaŵaga (achimakafilio) ŵakupedwa lipesa"
  15,9,Chisimu Uwwe ni Aŵala ŵatutulwisye Chikumbusyo (Qur’an) soni Uwwe chisimu chene tuchigose
  15,10,Soni chisimu chene twaatumisye (Achimitume) paujo penu (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) m’mikutula (jaŵandu) ŵandanda
  15,11,Ni nganijwaichililaga ntenga jwalijose ikaŵeje ŵaliji nkuntenda chipongwe
  15,12,Iyyoyopeyo tukuupitisyaga (nteto wachipongwewo) m’mitima mwa akuleŵa
  15,13,Ngakasajikulupililaga jalakwe (Qur’an) kutendaga pamasile payapite ilandanyo ya (ŵandu) ŵandanda (yaŵatite kapedwe ipotesi)
  15,14,"Soni tungaaugulile (achimakafilio) nnango wakwinani, ni kuŵa ŵanganyao ali nkukwela kwalakweko chitetete (mwaakusachila, kuti chiŵe chisimosimo cha Muhammadi ﷺ)"
  15,15,"Basi angatite: “Chisimu meso getu gantesile ndandagasi. (Ngwamba), nambo kuti uwwe ni ŵandu ŵakulogwa (tukuiona ikaliyo).”"
  15,16,"Soni chisimu chene tuŵisile kwinani ndondwa syekulungwakulungwa ni mwakwenda mwakwe, ni tukusalalisye kwa ŵaakuona"
  15,17,Ni tukugosile ku shetani jwalijose jwakuŵinjidwa
  15,18,"Ikaŵeje jwaakupikanilaga mwawiyi, basi papopo chisinga (cha moto) chakuonechela ni kunkuya"
  15,19,"Sano litaka twalijasesye ni kuŵika mwalakwemo yakunyichisya (gagali matumbi gausito), ni tumesisye mwalakwemo chindu chilichose chepimepime"
  15,20,Ni tum’bichile mwalakwemo yakulamila ŵanganyammwe ni ichindu yanganim’ba jenumanja kuti mpaka nkombole kuipatila lisiki (mpela inyama ni ilango ni ine yosope yaumi)
  15,21,"Ni pangali chindu chilichose ikaŵeje imatiilo yakwe ili Kukwetu, ni ngatukasachitulusyaga ikaŵeje kwa chipiimo chakumanyika"
  15,22,"Soni tukasasitumisyaga mbungo syakuŵelekasya (mawunde mesi gawula), basi ni tukasagwisyaga kuumila kwinani mesi (gawula), ni tukasampaga kumwa ŵanganyammwe galakwe, sano jenumanja ngaŵa ni ŵankugasungaga galakwe (mesigo)"
  15,23,"Soni chisimu Uwwe ni Aŵala ŵatukupeleka umi ni chiwa, soni Uwwe ni Ŵawinjila"
  15,24,"Soni pamasile patwamanyi kusyene ŵaŵalongolele mwa jenumanja (ŵaŵawile kala), soni pamasile patwamanyi kusyene ŵaasigalile (ŵaali chijumi kwisa soni ŵanganapagwe)"
  15,25,"Soni chisimu Ambuje ŵenu Ŵalakwe ni ŵatachasonganganya ŵanganyao, chisimu Ŵalakweo ni Ŵalunda lwakusokoka, Ŵakumanyilila nnope"
  15,26,Soni chisimu chene mundu twan’gumbile ni lilongo lyejumu lyakulilaga (nkuligombamo) lyakuumila m’matope gakupiililila geunde
  15,27,Sano lijini twaligumbile kala kuumila ku malamba ga moto gangali lyosi
  15,28,"Soni (kumbuchilani) katema kaŵaŵechete Ambuje ŵenu kwa Achimalaika kuti: “Chisimu Une tingumbe mundu ni lilongo lyejumu lyakulilaga (nkuligombamo) lyakuumila m’matope gakupiililila geunde.”"
  15,29,"“Sano patimale kunkolosya ni kumpepelela nsimu wakuuma Kukwangu, basi munsenjelemukuchile pakunsujudila.”"
  15,30,Basi ni ŵasujudu Achimalaika wosope ŵene nakamo
  15,31,Pangaŵaga Ibulisu; jwakanile kuti aŵe pamo ni akusujudu
  15,32,"(Allah) jwatite: “E mmwe Ibulisu! Chipali chichi kukwenu chintendekasisye kuti nkaŵa pamo ni akusujudu?”"
  15,33,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Une nganimba jwanti nikunsujudila mundu jwamun’gumbile ni lilongo lyejumu lyakulilaga (nkuligombamo) lyakuumila m’matope gakupiililila geunde.”"
  15,34,"(Allah) jwatite: “Basi kopokani mwalakwemo, mwanti chisimu mmwe (sano) n’di ŵakuŵinjidwa.”"
  15,35,“Soni chisimu pachanya penu pana malweso mpaka Lisiku Lyamalipilo.”
  15,36,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ambuje ŵangu! Mumbanitu lipesa (lyakuti ngawa) mpaka lisiku lyatachiukulidwa (m’malembe achiiumbe wosope).”"
  15,37,"(Allah) jwatite: “Basi chisimu mmwe n’di mwa akupedwa lipesa.”"
  15,38,"“Kwikanila lisiku lya ndema jakumanyika (jagombedwa lipenga lyandanda, pele ni patinchiwila).”"
  15,39,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ambuje ŵangu! Ligongo lyanti munechelele kusokonechela, basi chinasalalichisye kwene ŵanganyao pa chilambo (litala lyesokonechele), ni chinasokonesye kwene ŵanaose.”"
  15,40,“Pangaŵaga achikapolo Ŵenu ŵakuswejesyedwa mwa ŵanganyao.”
  15,41,"(Allah) jwatite: “Ali nilitala lya Kukwangu lyalili lyagoloka.”"
  15,42,"“Chisimu achikapolo Ŵangu nganinkola mmwejo pa ŵanganyao machili, ikaŵeje aŵala ŵatakankuyeje (mwakusaka kwao) mwa akusokonechela.”"
  15,43,Soni chisimu Jahannama ni malo gao gaakupedwa chilanga ŵanaose
  15,44,"Jikwete milango nsano najiŵili, nnango uliose ukwete liunjili mwa ŵanganyao lyegaŵidwegaŵidwe"
  15,45,Chisimu ŵaoga (wakun’jogopa Allah) tachiŵa m’Matimbe ga ku Mbepo ni sulo (syasichijilimaga chapasi pakwe)
  15,46,(Tachisalilidwa kuti) gajinjilani mwantendele n’di ŵagosedwa
  15,47,"Ni tuchityosya iwundo (ya uchimwa ni litima) yayaliji m’mitima mwao, tachiŵa (ŵakunonyelana) mwaulongo ali (atemi) pa itengu yauchimbichimbi mwakulolegana"
  15,48,"Ngagaja kwakwaya mwalakwemo masausyo galigose, soni ŵanganyao ngaaja koposyedwamo"
  15,49,"Mwatagulilani achikapolo Ŵangu yanti chisimu Une ni jwandi Jwakululuka kusyene, Jwachanasa channope"